Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路过这里的各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请投出您公正的一票…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是以能够保护国民安全的国王为目标的樱田茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我樱田茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为这次选举的候选人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把摄像机架好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连电视台都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是机会啊  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样大家都能听到你的宣言了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先第一个候选公约是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将监视摄像头废除…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给大家一个平静安稳的日常生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那样盯着我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此向大家保证…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经  不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜能够开始街头演说是很好
