Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假面英雄  玫瑰台风XX现在登场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1281,990)\fs54}Rose Typhoon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护人们安全的假面英雄玫瑰台风XX
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  其真实身份是班上第一冒失鬼花江的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就骗骗小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露的话花江会变成兔子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节目也会完结的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是知道了她的真实身份  大家都会感谢花江的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让茜做蒙面英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  将身份隐藏起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜也就能积极地去帮助别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在选举前将她的身份暴露的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能使她的人气急剧上升
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪着茜进行演说我意识到了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她继续以那种性格的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心将来她面对很多事时会很艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也明白茜正以自己的方式拼命想改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是能让她有大方站在别人面前的实际经验的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想可以慢慢增加她的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干扰眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一旦戴上就能让周围的人无法辨认的眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做蒙面英雄的时候  把这个作为变身道具使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是特意去生成出来的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得她只是从自己的房间里拿了副眼镜过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不相信我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谢谢  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我为了削减生成的成本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让效果只会在茜戴上时发动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  对于知道这副眼镜性能的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果会很薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不必勉强使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  会很小心地使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是和平时的感觉不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能是谁  茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的吧  修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  没有暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚说了「啊」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fs60\fscx85\fsp7.5\3c&H041515&\bord3\pos(1404,133.5)}茜FANCLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了正义所撒的谎吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴着眼镜的茜过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要骗她说是不认识的人哦  知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了茜姐姐的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时也是需要善意的谎言的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因为有不认识的女人在家里感到害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞  是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是茜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  吓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓了一跳啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙面英雄计划  正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  去救救它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它没法下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个高度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不能这么乱来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…莫非你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我是」？
