Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错呢  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(793.5,990)\fs54}Scarlet Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉当了绯红之花之后支持率上升了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  为什么隐藏了身份  我的支持率还会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因为演说的效果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
